♪Then I shall keep wearing my disguise♪

27
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:18,780
=Lies Never Lie=

28
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,870
Can you say something?

29
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,910
Where's my sister?

30
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:31,000
Can you say something?

31
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,280
The suspect, Zeng Xiang,

32
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,870
was arrested five years ago
for drug-related crimes.

33
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:54,310
So, he harbored hatred toward
Ning Jing, the police officer

34
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,520
who was on that case.

35
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:59,120
Thus, he sought revenge crazily.

36
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:02,240
Captain Ning Jing
from Criminal Investigation Team

37
00:03:02,470 --> 00:03:04,630
died on duty while solving this case.

38
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:08,680
We've lost the best police officer.

39
00:03:20,430 --> 00:03:22,360
You rejected Zhiyuan many times.

40
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,310
But that foolish child
still thinks naively

41
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,960
that it's not just friendship

42
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,630
between the two of you.

43
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:34,470
You can help me
explain it to Ning Zhiyuan.

44
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,240
But he doesn't believe me.

45
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,274
(Mochou, what are you doing?)

46
00:03:51,290 --> 00:03:52,698
(Mochou, pick up.)

47
00:03:52,698 --> 00:03:53,700
(Can we meet up?)

48
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,960
I'm looking for Mochou.

49
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,910
I know that she's back.

50
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:56,980
Right? She must be inside.

51
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,000
Zhiyuan.

52
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,870
Listen to me.

53
00:03:59,310 --> 00:03:59,960
She's not here.

54
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,310
She's out on a mission.

55
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:05,240
Where is she now?

56
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:08,190
You know

57
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,870
that we have rules.

58
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,310
He has left.

59
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,120
Mochou.

60
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,070
Hang in there.

61
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:30,070
Ning Jing!

62
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:30,800
Mochou.

63
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:32,120
Mochou.

64
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,000
Chief Jia.

65
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,560
I wish to apply for a transfer.

66
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:45,220
=Lies Never Lie=
=Episode 2=

67
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,510
I found her!

68
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,600
I found her before you.

69
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,560
That's because
we worked together very well.

70
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,190
Yifei, are you okay?

71
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:41,040
What took you so long?

72
00:05:41,330 --> 00:05:42,950
- I was scared.
- I came here right away.

73
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,360
Where's my sister?

74
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,830
Let me look at you.

75
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,240
Are you hurt?

76
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,680
Hang in there.

77
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,870
Ning Jing!

78
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:56,600
Mochou.

79
00:05:58,510 --> 00:05:59,480
Luckily, you are fine.

80
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,390
You are different from the female

81
00:06:20,390 --> 00:06:21,510
entrepreneur I imagined.

82
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,240
How am I different?

83
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:24,510
Way younger.

84
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:26,040
You look like a university student.

85
00:06:28,310 --> 00:06:29,750
I'll take that as a compliment.

86
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:33,120
Thank you, Officer Li.

87
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:35,990
Thank you for saving my girlfriend.

88
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:40,390
If it's okay,

89
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,480
we'll go to the hospital.

90
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,950
Do you know him?

91
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,600
Yes.

92
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:02,680
I do.

93
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:04,000
Let me reintroduce myself.

94
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,000
Ding Wei, from Team B.

95
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,920
I have things to do. Gotta go.

96
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:10,600
Okay.

97
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,190
Ms. Li.

98
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,070
You are amazing.

99
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,270
Can you teach me?

100
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:15,830
Will it be too late for someone like me

101
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:17,150
who has no psychology background?

102
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,950
Of course not.

103
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:18,800
Besides,

104
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,630
how did you find out from him

105
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:22,190
that she was on the fishing boat?

106
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:24,310
Well.

107
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,510
Tell us.

108
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:27,240
Tell us.

109
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:28,920
It's not that hard.

110
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,510
Since the beginning, Yuan Xi

111
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:32,630
has already set up
a countdown game of catch.

112
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:34,070
He just wants to play with the cops.

113
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:35,240
So, the more nervous we are,

114
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,240
the more excited he is.

115
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:40,270
So, you chatted with him
about geography.

116
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:43,950
Yes. But it was not
just a pointless chat.

117
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,310
I just roughly use

118
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:47,360
some locations in Baizhou

119
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:50,310
to eliminate some of the places
the hostage may be hidden.

120
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,120
I see.

121
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,310
You are amazing.

122
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:54,430
Can you teach me?

123
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,360
It was my first time

124
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,560
knowing the distance
from the east to the west

125
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,800
and from the south to the north.

126
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,870
I was shocked.

127
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:02,870
I firstly seeing
that kind of interrogation.

128
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:07,000
To be honest,
those were just random numbers.

129
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:07,920
What?

130
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:08,870
Yes.

131
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:11,510
Until we talked about his childhood.

132
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:12,720
I found that he reacted.

133
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:15,000
So, I asked him
if he wanted water or coffee.

134
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,360
And I made the decision for him.

135
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,120
At that moment,

136
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,680
I succeeded in bringing him

137
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,870
into a game I set.

138
00:08:20,210 --> 00:08:21,310
Actually, psychology can't

139
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,800
be the only basis in solving cases.

140
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:25,430
It can only provide more clues
and give a direction.

141
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:26,270
It's an aid.

142
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,390
What?

143
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,270
Okay. I got it.

144
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:32,480
Yuan Xi committed suicide.

145
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:33,910
There's poison in his teeth.

146
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,480
So, he was ready

147
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,080
to die

148
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,320
before telling you the location
of the hostage.

149
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:46,030
But how is that related to "seven"?

150
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,510
Yuan Xi

151
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:48,360
is quite pitiful.

152
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:50,750
When he was seven,

153
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:52,750
he injected his mother with an overdose,

154
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:53,750
leading to her death.

155
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:55,030
It traumatized him.

156
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:58,240
That's one of the reasons
why he was mentally twisted.

157
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:01,320
Yes.

158
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:03,750
The six previous victims

159
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,480
were related to "seven" as well.

160
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,960
And all those six deceased

161
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,240
sold addictive products.

162
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:13,270
But Tianxiang Group
is a pharmaceutical company.

163
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,150
Many medications
can lead to addiction too.

164
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:20,360
Captain Ding.

165
00:09:21,270 --> 00:09:22,510
Thank you for being my eyes.

166
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,200
Zhiyuan.

167
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,630
Zhiyuan.

168
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,390
You are awake.

169
00:09:56,790 --> 00:10:00,240
Why do I feel like you are distracted?

170
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,200
What's wrong?

171
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,440
Just now, I was thinking

172
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,960
what I would do
if I lost you forever.

173
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,390
You dummy.

174
00:10:09,030 --> 00:10:09,840
Look.

175
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:12,510
I'm all well now.

176
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:15,750
Are you done peeling?

177
00:10:28,670 --> 00:10:29,480
It's so sweet.

178
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,270
Zhiyuan.

179
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,200
The police officer just now,

180
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:39,670
Li Mochou,

181
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:41,600
do you know her?

182
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,870
Chief Jia.

183
00:10:54,870 --> 00:10:56,670
I spent one year looking for Mochou.

184
00:10:56,670 --> 00:10:58,120
I sent her countless messages.

185
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,250
She didn't reply any of them.

186
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:00,840
She didn't go home too.

187
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,120
Why she's acting like this?

188
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,850
As if she has changed
into another person.

189
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:08,240
Our company has decided
to collaborate with Thailand.

190
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,480
I'll leave tomorrow.

191
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:15,000
She used to be

192
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,720
my sister's colleague.

193
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,240
The three of us were very close.

194
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,790
I haven't seen her in a long time.

195
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:23,750
She's like an old friend.

196
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,600
It's okay. I'm just asking.

197
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:29,750
You don't have to tell me everything.

198
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,550
I trust you.

199
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:35,390
Mr. Qiu, it was a near-miss
for Ms. Luo this time.

200
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,510
Yes.

201
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:37,440
Her ward is there.

202
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,270
Okay.

203
00:11:40,150 --> 00:11:41,080
Mr. Ning, you are here.

204
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:44,080
Shouldn't I be here, Mr. Meng?

205
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:47,320
How's Yifei right now?

206
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,120
She's doing okay.

207
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:50,360
She's resting now.

208
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,320
Let me introduce.

209
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:54,600
He is Mr. Qiu from the Dazhou Group.

210
00:11:54,810 --> 00:11:57,200
He is Tianxiang's strategic
business partner, Ning Zhiyuan.

211
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,000
Mr. Ning.

212
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,200
- Hello.
- Hello.

213
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:04,000
Is Yifei still sleeping?

214
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,390
Yes.

215
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,440
Mr. Qiu.

216
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,790
I'm really sorry.

217
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:09,910
Ms. Luo is still sleeping.

218
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:12,360
I'll ask my assistant
to take you to the resting area.

219
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:14,910
- I'll leave you to it.
- Let me have a few words with Mr. Ning.

220
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:16,150
- Okay.
- Thank you.

221
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,200
Zhiyuan.

222
00:12:18,550 --> 00:12:19,150
Come.

223
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:21,870
I hear that you've been
on business trips.

224
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,510
Yes. I just came back from Xiamen.

225
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:25,440
You've worked hard.

226
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,630
Ning Zhiyuan.

227
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,840
If I were you,

228
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:00,240
I would murder Yuan Xi.

229
00:13:12,210 --> 00:13:13,600
He has been arrested by the police.

230
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:15,910
If it weren't for them,
Yifei would be dead now.

231
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:18,670
I've always known that you are a coward.

232
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:39,480
Let me tell you.

233
00:13:40,670 --> 00:13:41,840
Yifei is not an ordinary girl.

234
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:44,600
You better stay away from her.

235
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:07,910
Hey.

236
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,000
Captain Yue.

237
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:11,720
I saw someone delivering
a banner to us just now.

238
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:13,320
I've heard about it.

239
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:15,360
Look.

240
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,390
Banners are great.

241
00:14:17,650 --> 00:14:20,200
(Serving the People without Fear)
But things are not one-sided.

242
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,150
(Serve the People)

243
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:22,360
What do fewer banners mean?

244
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,150
It means that there are fewer cases.

245
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,390
Fewer cases mean better public security.

246
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,600
Right?

247
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:30,200
We have to be humble

248
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,600
even after achieving great things.

249
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,550
Right? Someone fights for fame.

250
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,120
What do you fight for?

251
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:38,790
I fight for the people.

252
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:39,790
- Or what else?
- Hah.

253
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:42,440
Ms. Wei.

254
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:45,390
This is the information
for the meeting later.

255
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,360
Ms. Li, let me pour you a cup of coffee.

256
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,080
You don't have to be so kind.

257
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:51,720
By the way.

258
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,150
Yes?

259
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:54,630
It seems like you are interested
in psychology.

260
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:57,240
I've compiled
some information on psychology.

261
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,270
You can take a look.

262
00:14:58,270 --> 00:15:00,510
I don't know if you'll
be interested in studying it.

263
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:01,910
Thank you.

264
00:15:02,030 --> 00:15:04,000
Also, if I want to drink coffee,

265
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:04,870
I'll make it myself.

266
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:05,960
You don't have to do it.

267
00:15:06,150 --> 00:15:06,960
Okay.

268
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:15,790
Mr. Meng.

269
00:15:18,510 --> 00:15:19,320
This way, please.

270
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:22,550
Chief Ou.

271
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,240
Ding Wei.

272
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,440
Yue Qun.

273
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,750
- Master.
- Come.

274
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,510
Let me introduce this man to you.

275
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:32,080
He is Meng Zhengyi,
from Tianxiang Group.

276
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:34,320
He's here to express his thanks.

277
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:37,480
I'm here on behalf
of the group and myself

278
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,030
to thank all of you today.

279
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,670
Thank you for rescuing Ms. Luo.

280
00:15:40,950 --> 00:15:41,360
Thank you.

281
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,670
We were just doing our duty.

282
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,000
This...

