00:15:46,350 --> 00:15:47,030
You are too kind.

284
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:47,630
No need for it.

285
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:48,250
You deserve it.

286
00:15:48,260 --> 00:15:49,320
This is huge.

287
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:52,240
A role model in solving cases

288
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,270
and serving the people.

289
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:54,840
To...

290
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:57,080
Officer Li Mochou.

291
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,270
They wrote it wrongly.

292
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:01,270
Nonsense.

293
00:16:01,270 --> 00:16:03,840
It's because of everyone
that we managed to save Ms. Luo.

294
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:10,840
It's wrong.

295
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,670
Hang it up.

296
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,080
Keep quiet.

297
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:13,750
Ms. Li.

298
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:14,630
Hang it up?

299
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:16,600
I've heard about everything.

300
00:16:17,030 --> 00:16:18,030
If it wasn't for you,

301
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,200
they wouldn't have found
that boat quickly. Thank you.

302
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,270
You are too kind.

303
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:25,120
You solved the case with psychology.

304
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:26,080
You are extraordinary.

305
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:29,320
Are you new to Baizhou, Ms. Li?

306
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:30,440
Yes.

307
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:33,360
If you need any help
or face any trouble,

308
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,390
you can come to me.

309
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:36,790
I can't solve cases.

310
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,320
But I can do my best to help you

311
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:40,840
run some errands.

312
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:43,030
I see.

313
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:49,910
Meng Zhengyi.

314
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:51,480
Thank you.

315
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:53,000
Please take care of us.

316
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:53,940
Thank you.

317
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,440
Chief Ou, it's almost time.

318
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,870
I'll get ready with the meeting.

319
00:16:58,870 --> 00:16:59,670
Okay.

320
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:03,960
Chief Ou.

321
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:06,590
I won't disturb you further
from doing your work.

322
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:07,160
See you.

323
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:07,550
Bye.

324
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:08,160
Goodbye.

325
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,170
Okay. Let me see you out.

326
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:10,830
Goodbye.

327
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,030
Mr. Meng.

328
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:17,260
(A Role Model in Solving Cases)

329
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:33,680
Welcome.

330
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:36,680
Welcome.

331
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:50,920
Sir.

332
00:17:51,110 --> 00:17:52,030
Are you okay?

333
00:17:54,350 --> 00:17:55,160
Madam.

334
00:17:58,590 --> 00:17:59,400
Sir.

335
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:03,880
Help!

336
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:06,310
Anybody? Help!

337
00:18:37,070 --> 00:18:38,270
Captain Ding.

338
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:39,550
Are you not coming in tomorrow?

339
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:40,920
Why act so diligent?

340
00:18:43,270 --> 00:18:44,310
You're staying here?

341
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:45,880
Exploit the station?

342
00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:52,000
Before I came here,

343
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,900
I already rented a house.

344
00:18:53,910 --> 00:18:55,310
But I don't like it after seeing it.

345
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:57,830
So, I've decided to stay
at the station for two more days.

346
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,270
You are too picky.

347
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,270
Pack your things.

348
00:19:02,270 --> 00:19:03,240
You can stay at my house.

349
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,750
I don't want to intrude.

350
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,510
You don't seem reluctant.

351
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:13,110
Thank you.

352
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:36,160
Oh.

353
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,200
Captain Ding.

354
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:41,000
Is Meng Zhengyi, from Tianxiang Group

355
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,400
close to the station?

356
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:46,070
Tianxiang Group
is the leading enterprise of Baizhou.

357
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:47,960
So, our superiors take it seriously.

358
00:19:49,110 --> 00:19:50,720
But I have received some information.

359
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,480
Although Luo Yifei

360
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,480
is the chairwoman of Tianxiang Group,

361
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:57,720
the man who holds real power
is Meng Zhengyi.

362
00:19:58,440 --> 00:19:59,000
I see.

363
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,830
Have you dabbled in psychology before?

364
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:06,680
I studied criminal psychology
when I was in the police academy.

365
00:20:07,110 --> 00:20:08,480
What does it have to do with him?

366
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:09,680
Of course it does.

367
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,440
At least he knows a bit of it.

368
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:12,400
Otherwise,

369
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:14,750
why he gave me such a huge banner

370
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:16,720
on my first day
at Baizhou Police Station?

371
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:18,200
I'm very sure he knows

372
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:21,000
you are the real backbone
of Baizhou Police Station.

373
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:23,480
So, he was trying
to drive a wedge between us

374
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:25,680
by using the most common
human emotion, jealousy.

375
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:28,480
I don't think

376
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,310
you should worry.

377
00:20:30,110 --> 00:20:31,240
With how blatant he was,

378
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,990
I could tell that he had
an ulterior motive.

379
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:35,510
Hello?

380
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:39,160
Okay. I got it.

381
00:20:41,030 --> 00:20:41,960
We can't go home now.

382
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:44,200
Let's go to the crime scene.

383
00:20:44,230 --> 00:20:45,680
A murder in the Haitian Grand Hotel.

384
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:53,070
Bao Xijie, male.

385
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:55,110
Age, 54. The chairman of Kunpeng Group.

386
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:56,480
He Xin, female.

387
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:58,640
Age, 51. Bai Xijie's wife.

388
00:20:59,100 --> 00:20:59,830
Bao Wenxuan, male.

389
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:00,510
Age, 22.

390
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:02,070
Bao Xijie and He Xin's only son.

391
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:04,480
It was Bao Xijie's
54th birthday yesterday.

392
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:06,070
The family came here to celebrate.

393
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:09,920
All three victims have
dozens of stab wounds.

394
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:11,090
Large blood vessels ruptured.

395
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,510
They died from blood loss.

396
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,550
Further examination is needed.

397
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:15,880
A crime of passion.

398
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:16,640
A vendetta.

399
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:19,000
This is too vicious.

400
00:21:19,310 --> 00:21:20,920
This is not a common vendetta.

401
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,550
This is deep hatred.

402
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:34,030
Captain Ding, Liu, take a look at this.

403
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:36,070
What is this?

404
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:43,590
After he killed them,

405
00:21:43,590 --> 00:21:45,480
the murderer must
have taken something away.

406
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:48,070
Judging from the shape,
it can be a luggage bag.

407
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,510
Such a brutal killing method.

408
00:21:55,010 --> 00:21:56,350
It must have caused quite a stir.

409
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:57,330
Where are the witnesses?

410
00:21:57,350 --> 00:21:58,640
This is the worst part.

411
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,110
This hotel

412
00:22:00,110 --> 00:22:01,250
is very well enclosed.

413
00:22:01,260 --> 00:22:02,150
Good sound insulation.

414
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:03,790
No one noticed anything
until the server

415
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:04,790
brought their food over.

416
00:22:05,270 --> 00:22:06,160
This is a big hotel

417
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:06,790
with crowds.

418
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:08,160
But no one noticed anything?

419
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,440
Ms. Wei.

420
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:12,720
This is the record of everyone
who came here yesterday.

421
00:22:13,310 --> 00:22:14,550
Including staff, customers,

422
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:16,000
the pick-up of the kitchen,

423
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:16,960
and the take-out.

424
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:18,550
Nothing seems out of sorts.

425
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:21,440
Take it back and check.

426
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:21,790
Okay.

427
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:22,510
The CCTV footage?

428
00:22:23,030 --> 00:22:24,480
We didn't find any suspicious men.

429
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:27,240
This is such a mystery.

430
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:29,590
The murderer appeared out of thin air,

431
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,680
murdered three people,

432
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:31,920
and vanished.

433
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:41,270
Impossible.

434
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,270
When I get changed just now,

435
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,720
I took a look around this floor.

436
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:47,590
There are dozens of CCTV cameras
on this floor alone.

437
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,880
And the server left
for only five minutes.

438
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:53,070
He killed all three people
within five minutes

439
00:22:53,350 --> 00:22:55,400
without making a noise.

440
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:58,400
This murderer must be very calm.

441
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:01,880
Besides, he must have visited
this place again and again

442
00:23:02,030 --> 00:23:03,070
to plan out his murder.

443
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:07,920
But the crime scene looks chaotic.

444
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:11,960
These two aspects
are very contradictory.

445
00:23:14,010 --> 00:23:16,400
Is it possible that the murderer
had everything planned out,

446
00:23:16,790 --> 00:23:18,590
but lost control when he saw

447
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:19,790
his enemies?

448
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,240
No.

449
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:25,350
The murdered stabbed them messily
to create an illusion.

450
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,000
By the way,

451
00:23:27,590 --> 00:23:29,880
is there anything in common
between the wounds of them?

452
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,680
Ms. Li is right.

453
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:32,480
Look.

454
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:34,440
Their carotid arteries were severed.

455
00:23:35,550 --> 00:23:37,550
But the stab wounds
on their bodies are messy

456
00:23:37,550 --> 00:23:38,590
with different depths.

457
00:23:39,350 --> 00:23:41,310
But the wounds
on the carotid artery were clean.

458
00:23:41,310 --> 00:23:42,200
A fatal stab.

459
00:23:58,440 --> 00:23:59,350
Any news?

460
00:24:11,550 --> 00:24:13,110
Ms. Li, what's wrong?

461
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,960
Let me summarize it.

462
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,310
This is not a crime of passion.

463
00:24:21,110 --> 00:24:22,240
He's professional.

464
00:24:24,270 --> 00:24:25,880
A professional assassin?

465
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:32,270
Come in.

466
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:42,960
I never thought

467
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:45,440
that your house would be so clean.

468
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,550
It's fine.

469
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:48,590
I didn't clean it.

470
00:24:48,590 --> 00:24:50,880
My parents will clean my house
every now and then.

471
00:24:53,110 --> 00:24:54,110
You can sleep in my room.

472
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:55,720
Well... No.

473
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,790
I can sleep on the sofa.

474
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:58,750
Stop it.

475
00:24:58,750 --> 00:24:59,680
We have a guest room.

476
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:01,160
I'll take a shower first.

477
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,550
You should unpack and take a rest.

478
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:03,880
We'll analyze the case tomorrow.

479
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:07,030
You should've told me earlier.

480
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:26,790
Mochou.

481
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:27,270
Yes?

482
00:25:27,310 --> 00:25:28,830
Let me tell you something.

483
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:30,200
Okay.

484
00:25:30,590 --> 00:25:32,550
When two objects connect,

485
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,960
something will be transferred.

486
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:35,680
When something is taken away,

487
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:37,550
something will be left behind.

488
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:38,640
Okay.

489
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:39,720
Have some water.

490
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:43,680
This is too complicated.

491
00:25:44,110 --> 00:25:45,720
To put it simply,

492
00:25:45,720 --> 00:25:47,310
you'll always pay

493
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:48,350
for what you've done.

494
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:50,480
Don't make it sound so mysterious.

495
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,440
Good comprehensive skills.

496
00:25:52,550 --> 00:25:53,640
Of course.

497
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:54,960
Wait.

498
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:56,030
Let me ask you this.

499
00:25:56,270 --> 00:25:58,240
If we follow your logic,

500
00:25:58,310 --> 00:25:59,640
why are there still

501
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:01,510
so many unsolved cases in this world?

502
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:05,880
Because we are not attentive enough.

503
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:08,440
So, we haven't found the clues.

504
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,750
You're attentive enough.

505
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:10,270
Oh, my.

506
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:12,880
You are the most
attentive person in the world.

507
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:15,030
Looks like being a doc
has changed you.

508
00:26:15,030 --> 00:26:16,550
You are the most attentive one.

509
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,920
How dare you kick your master.

510
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,830
No.

511
00:26:18,830 --> 00:26:20,030
What is the meaning of this?

512
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:30,440
Li Mochou, are you done unpacking?

513
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:34,070
I'm coming.

514
00:26:40,830 --> 00:26:41,640
Bao Xijie

515
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,880
has a criminal history.

516
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:47,920
A criminal history?

517
00:26:48,270 --> 00:26:49,550
He was earning black money.

518
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:51,920
But he changed after he became successful.

519
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,270
And he did a lot of charity.

520
00:26:53,590 --> 00:26:54,680
The real kind of charity.

521
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:58,880
It means that this person felt guilty

522
00:26:58,880 --> 00:26:59,830
about his previous acts.

523
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:02,510
So, he must have lived
with a sense of atonement.

524
00:27:03,100 --> 00:27:05,070
People like him shouldn't
have too many enemies.

525
00:27:06,310 --> 00:27:07,790
We investigated his social relations.

526
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,160
We didn't find anything abnormal.

527
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:14,310
We didn't find any useless clues
at the crime scene too.

528
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:16,590
Sigh.

529
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:18,070
I can't find any clues.

530
00:27:19,110 --> 00:27:21,440
I don't believe in a perfect crime.

531
00:27:25,510 --> 00:27:27,310
I have a way to catch him.

532
00:27:35,310 --> 00:27:35,920
This is...

533
00:27:41,790 --> 00:27:42,590
How is it?

534
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,400
Any news?

535
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:13,480
Carotid artery laceration.

536
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:19,310
If nothing was blocking the blade,

537
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:22,000
I would be dead.

538
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,880
What are you saying?

539
00:28:25,590 --> 00:28:26,880
The murderer who assassinated me

540
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:29,790
might be the same man

541
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,000
who murdered Bao Xijie.

542
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:36,200
What is your plan?

543
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:40,160
He didn't manage to kill me.

544
00:28:40,480 --> 00:28:43,030
If I show up in front of him again,

545
00:28:43,510 --> 00:28:44,990
I'm sure he'll come for me once more.

546
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:46,830
What's the reason?

547
00:28:48,350 --> 00:28:50,070
Back then, he only cut me once.

548
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:52,640
And he left without a backward glance.

549
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:54,680
If he had cut me again,

550
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:56,070
I would be dead on the spot.

551
00:28:56,750 --> 00:28:58,030
What does that mean?

552
00:28:58,400 --> 00:28:59,350
He's confident.

553
00:28:59,790 --> 00:29:00,720
Extremely confident.

554
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,880
And me being alive

555
00:29:02,880 --> 00:29:04,880
is the biggest challenge
for his confidence.

556
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:07,550
Based on the current clues that we have,

557
00:29:07,550 --> 00:29:09,720
it's hard for us to capture
this professional assassin.

558
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:11,550
So, we can only throw out the bait

559
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:12,590
and let him to take a bite.

560
00:29:12,790 --> 00:29:13,510
No.

561
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:16,790
I will be fine.

562
00:29:16,790 --> 00:29:17,350
Impossible.

563
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:24,270
Captain Ding.

564
00:29:24,270 --> 00:29:25,200
Think of this

565
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,960
as doing me a favor.

566
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:30,240
This man is very important to me.

567
